The paper deals with video classification using deep convolutional networks, which is a topic closely related to computer vision (cs.CV). The authors also discuss the use of neural networks for classification, which falls under machine learning (cs.MM) and deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves the use of large datasets and efficient processing, which could be categorized under information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
